Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候已久的时刻到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了证明许多英灵并非平白丧生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2号机？在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米岛的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为再次高揭ZION的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦为成就“星尘”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门啊！我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}激突战域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这就是“星尘”吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的，不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多还真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛大人，时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今就动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向右5度，第2战速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是凯风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防艇还没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ES-11请求增援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5号闸门不能使用吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内还有船员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS不能出动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害区域42%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的MS竟做出这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还事情没了断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将本舰转向金米岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没了断…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动啊，左腕不能动了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐，太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出预期的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我们这三年也有回报了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那些游手好闲的家伙们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是所谓的恶梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，待会见，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在预订地点恭候您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的不堪一击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正下方？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多，听到吗？回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能听到的吧，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你忘了，我也绝不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次那个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没了断前我不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这只是为我的胜仗锦上添花而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过对你没什么可多费唇舌的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对，卡多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多，听不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各舰前往第10区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12号闸门在封锁中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SL的残存部队集结到L23
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7区域损害率87%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各舰队都受到很大的损害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约有2/3无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就算只剩1/3的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍远占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而相反的他们已用掉了底牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将旗舰转为“兹隆”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后进行周围巡哨及舰队的重新编制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比昂来电“前来救援”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还来干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说港区很混乱反而会添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取独立的索敌攻击部队所应有的自由行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足了吧，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那对2号机被夺走的我们而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是耻辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来把他惹火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,582
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就听听看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨是战斗起源的本因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但凭怨恨支持战斗的人打不倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我站在“义”字之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做为齿轮而战的人不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左腕不能动？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手长进了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这两人非得战斗不可呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，主摄像机…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我和你的价值观终究是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，脱离吧，快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏，快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 Core Fighter不能用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你叫浦木吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不会忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信已中断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉也平安脱离了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是草莓9号，草莓9号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在125地点巡哨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉眼确认了移动中的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓9号请继续巡哨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金米岛的事就像假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那像是鲸鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么啦，摩拉，没头没脑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像平时的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂头丧气地躲在房里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我失去了1号机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对妮娜而言是因为同时失去了1号和2号机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅如此吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，只有你能鼓励她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是高兹，听到请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人应答吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是高兹，听到请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，被干扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座殖民地由我们殖民地公社管理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是宇宙住民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地可说是我们生活的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM所引发的事全都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两架GUNDAM都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴你能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，今后该怎么办？妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地球也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宏一起的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不认为一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多的…他的态度…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星尘”仍然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再提那个人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今后战斗仍将持续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过投入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至渗透到身体之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想忘掉这一切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是莱因巴克1号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达与巡哨机失去联络的地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都平安无事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被联邦查觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派出狼群
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露馅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎太迟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS全机退避完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰主炮一起射击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持殖民地？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时爆破了两座殖民地的镜面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持无人的殖民地想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找两位来不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想你们听听我今后的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上我认为“星尘”的本质目前尚未显露出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说金米岛袭击可能是某种前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则迪拉兹为什么发表那样的演说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是恐吓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遵从贾布罗的高云将军的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定续行对迪拉兹舰队的战斗行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将GUNDAM的1号机和2号机运到了澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为需要做重力状态下地面测试的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那两架吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不在我管辖之内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在…3号机…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若以中尉的资历加上妮娜小姐技术的支持…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，请务必让我担任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，那完全是另一种机型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰已变更了航向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往正于3-5-B地点为测试而航行的“玫瑰人生”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有紧急情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持殖民地？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这镜面爆破是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜面？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩1分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我想像得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自失去一片镜面的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重心就会偏移，会产生回转倾斜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久它们就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会相撞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然，相撞的殖民地会彼此弹开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个会被月球重力所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对月球的殖民地坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将此事报告金米岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，让本舰也转向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个位置赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒殖民地相撞时的放电
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传来殖民地相撞的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1战速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一座殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定会向月球的拉格朗治点坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道情况会如何变化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在先去把GUNDAM…

Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.63,0:25:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预    告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.27,0:25:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星尘”在等离子空间觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.30,0:25:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球牵引着孤独的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.70,0:25:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在需要的是时间
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.78,0:25:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比昂为取得GUNDAM3号机造访了“玫瑰人生”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.49,0:25:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时钟永无停止的指针
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.35,0:25:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木焦躁的心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.42,0:25:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在耸立的GUNDAM3号机眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.20,0:25:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间在迫使妮娜下决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.42,0:25:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}“玫瑰人生”

